Make sure all the ingredients are cold.  Combine them.  Let sit at least 1 hour.  Serve.

Makes 16 half cup servings.  You can use Raisins instead of Craisins.  You can use Peas instead of Edamame.  You can give it a Oriental taste by subbing soy sauce for the mustard and rice vinegar for the balsamic.  You can add Smoked Turkey too.
